# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — Roadmap

Planned/desired work and **who is doing what**. This is the coordination surface — check it before
starting, claim what you take, and don't duplicate.

## How to use this (claim before you start)
1. Pick an item, set its **Status → 🚧** and **Owner** to your name + branch (e.g. `kc / feat-thing`).
2. **Commit that change first and push** so collaborators see the claim before you sink time in.
3. When it ships: move a one-line summary to `CHANGELOG.md` (newest first) and either delete the row
   or mark it ✅.
4. If you abandon it, set Status back to 🔲 and clear Owner.

**Status:** 🔲 Todo · 🚧 In progress · ✅ Done (pending move to CHANGELOG) · 🧊 Deferred / idea

